title: Do Make Say Think - & Yet & Yet [2002-Album]
description:
& Yet & Yet is the third full-length release from Toronto noise cherubs Do Make Say Think.  The album sticks to the old DMST format in that it is totally excellent, but aside from this it sounds refreshingly new and relatively untouched by the influence of their previous albums, shedding its dubby, space-rock skin and emerging an altogether different post-rock animal.
